{"tid":321941,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"窮撚入大學揀科，學人講乜撚興趣","createTime":"2017-07-14T13:04:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-16T11:29:11.000Z","uid":56498,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3c273fe4c2201fe2482de975171c03cdc47316e8","tid":321941,"uid":56498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T13:04:05.000Z","msg":"對窮撚嚟講，讀書向來都係為左令你人生出路多幾個選擇，而唔撚係豪使十幾廿萬比你happy四年囉<br />\n<br />\n到你讀完專科，做左有錢有大把假期的專業人士（乜鳩會計果類就食屎喇，有錢無命享），辭職hea足兩年去睇書都仲得喇！想識d學究嘅，你有錢嘅，再慢慢返嚟讀返幾個興趣科master都仲得添。<br />\n<br />\n揀興趣科會點？咪好似小弟咁撚樣囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 日日朝九晚十，要錢無錢，要時間無時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />返到屋企淨係想沖涼訓覺，係偶然放大假先睇到下書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f3a6f3aff2ce93f53cd573ffab6051aa5a1e444","tid":321941,"uid":58099,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T13:08:05.000Z","msg":"成世15k 已滿足<br />\n<br />\n做人不要太貪婪"},{"pid":"6a70bd7295b6fadab1ba11ef02a3baa5090192ac","tid":321941,"uid":56498,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T13:15:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成世15k 已滿足<br />\n<br />\n做人不要太貪婪</blockquote><br />\n咁你第日住邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e39d05de9198465cec860cb1d604117877eaa36","tid":321941,"uid":22302,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T16:00:22.000Z","msg":"其實master你讀mphil既話係大學比返錢你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢d都唔知仲學人講興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3975ce97890d45b5730e7a9d2681f42a9f23b6a2","tid":321941,"uid":56498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T17:07:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實master你讀mphil既話係大學比返錢你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢d都唔知仲學人講興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n請問大學生有幾多人會讀得上mphil 或者 PHD，然後順利入到大學教職呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d17d3de86539428c87ec05fe4550267a668c5f7","tid":321941,"uid":22302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T20:18:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實master你讀mphil既話係大學比返錢你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢d都唔知仲學人講興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n請問大學生有幾多人會讀得上mphil 或者 PHD，然後順利入到大學教職呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁就唔關興唔興趣事，而係你自己垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"327ec239e576320d60560f0ca3011674ada1bbb3","tid":321941,"uid":85093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T01:25:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>對窮撚嚟講，讀書向來都係為左令你人生出路多幾個選擇，而唔撚係豪使十幾廿萬比你happy四年囉<br />\n<br />\n到你讀完專科，做左有錢有大把假期的專業人士（乜鳩會計果類就食屎喇，有錢無命享），辭職hea足兩年去睇書都仲得喇！想識d學究嘅，你有錢嘅，再慢慢返嚟讀返幾個興趣科master都仲得添。<br />\n<br />\n揀興趣科會點？咪好似小弟咁撚樣囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 日日朝九晚十，要錢無錢，要時間無時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />返到屋企淨係想沖涼訓覺，係偶然放大假先睇到下書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咩興趣科"},{"pid":"08cc76fb578bbd3696dbb6e5b49f833684c2fdd9","tid":321941,"uid":36046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T12:40:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實master你讀mphil既話係大學比返錢你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢d都唔知仲學人講興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n請問大學生有幾多人會讀得上mphil 或者 PHD，然後順利入到大學教職呢<